<subSubSection id="E908EBD2EC5CAA7288EBB401ADEE2138" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="AC260EAEDFFD0307F61233C82110ED19" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Known host and distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F9B773651326242439EF585770BB9D75" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">
Tropical and subtropical regions of Central and South America, Africa, Asia, Oceania and North America. The species were found as saprobes on 
<taxonomicName id="BC7FE54090BD7CE1B8431FE3DF764AAC" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Acanthaceae" genus="Hermatomyces" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="" order="Pleosporales" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="family">Acanthaceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="85B281A1EFCF6597381482E754460927" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Apocynaceae" genus="Hermatomyces" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="" order="Pleosporales" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="family">Apocynaceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="F05D011DC48066FBD51E3486E2018176" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Arecaceae" genus="Hermatomyces" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="" order="Pleosporales" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="family">Arecaceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="B6E20428BF519750863D65D530EFEABF" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hermatomyces" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="" order="Pleosporales" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="family">Asteraceae</taxonomicName>
, 
